01:25:47,456 --> 01:25:48,514
I love pie.

1243
01:25:48,824 --> 01:25:50,018
I like you.

1244
01:25:50,325 --> 01:25:54,762
I'll bring you nine pies to take with you.
A pie for every day.

1245
01:25:55,063 --> 01:25:57,224
I don't want any pies.

1246
01:25:57,466 --> 01:26:00,128
It's my pleasure. They'll keep.

1247
01:26:01,903 --> 01:26:03,234
Don't. Really.

1248
01:26:03,705 --> 01:26:06,173
Don't bring me anything.

1249
01:26:12,147 --> 01:26:13,978
Oh, my God!

1250
01:26:19,554 --> 01:26:20,543
Oh, my God.

1251
01:26:20,856 --> 01:26:22,016
It's unbelievable.

1252
01:26:22,324 --> 01:26:24,315
My prosecutor just sat down.

1253
01:26:24,559 --> 01:26:26,550
Look. Don't look!

1254
01:26:26,928 --> 01:26:28,156
