Don't look! Back.

1267
01:27:14,843 --> 01:27:17,277
Okay. Suck that up.

1268
01:27:23,285 --> 01:27:24,877
It's long.

1269
01:27:25,287 --> 01:27:28,120
Bite down now, please. Please bite.

1270
01:27:30,692 --> 01:27:31,681
Bite.

1271
01:27:34,663 --> 01:27:35,322
Done.

1272
01:27:37,432 --> 01:27:38,763
She makes me nervous.

1273
01:27:38,900 --> 01:27:40,595
I'm going to the ladies' room.

1274
01:27:42,304 --> 01:27:44,670
