1275
01:27:44,739 --> 01:27:46,001
...you've changed.

1276
01:27:52,547 --> 01:27:54,139
You're Daniel's prosecutor.

1277
01:27:56,718 --> 01:27:58,743
I want you to know he's wonderful.

1278
01:28:01,389 --> 01:28:02,287
You are?

1279
01:28:02,657 --> 01:28:03,419
Julia.

1280
01:28:03,491 --> 01:28:04,549
Pretty name.

1281
01:28:06,061 --> 01:28:08,086
-Nice to meet you.
-What did I say?

1282
01:28:10,532 --> 01:28:12,932
So you don't forget, I bring these.

1283
01:28:13,635 --> 01:28:15,330
You've got nine pies in here.

1284
01:28:15,437 --> 01:28:18,372
-Will that be enough for you?
-I didn't want these.

1285
01:28:18,540 --> 01:28:20,201
You told me to make them.

1286
01:28:20,408 --> 01:28:21,932
I did not.

1287
01:28:22,110 --> 01:28:23,737
-You said that.
-No.

1288
01:28:23,845 --> 01:28:24,812
Yes, you did.

1289
