-I know you think I've got it together.
-You do.

1298
01:29:23,872 --> 01:29:25,703
No, not quite.

1299
01:29:26,841 --> 01:29:30,208
But one thing I do know how to do
is make things work.

1300
01:29:30,345 --> 01:29:33,371
I can take a situation
and just make it okay.

1301
01:29:33,448 --> 01:29:35,382
I've always been able to do that.

1302
01:29:35,884 --> 01:29:37,476
But it's work.

1303
01:29:38,620 --> 01:29:40,110
