1306
01:29:45,660 --> 01:29:47,059
...but it's--

1307
01:29:50,465 --> 01:29:51,898
Effortless.

1308
01:29:55,937 --> 01:29:58,462
I've never, ever had that before.

1309
01:29:58,606 --> 01:30:00,164
Tell me about it.

1310
01:30:00,275 --> 01:30:02,368
I didn't think it would happen to me.

1311
