-Better this than nothing.
-I guess.

1314
01:30:15,090 --> 01:30:17,024
Want to spend the night with me?

1315
01:30:18,460 --> 01:30:20,621
More than anything in the world.

1316
01:30:21,663 --> 01:30:23,995
Good. Come on, let's go.

1317
01:30:25,900 --> 01:30:28,869
I don't think I can. I don't think I should.

1318
01:30:30,071 --> 01:30:31,197
Why?

1319
01:30:31,940 --> 01:30:32,907
Because.

1320
01:30:34,609 --> 01:30:39,308
This is already better
than any sex I've ever had. Ever.

1321
01:30:41,182 --> 01:30:44,208
I don't want to screw it up. Literally.

1322
01:30:44,285 --> 01:30:47,277
-How do you know what will happen?
-I don't.

1323
01:30:47,355 --> 01:30:50,347
Let's say it's the most amazing thing ever.

1324
01:30:50,458 --> 01:30:52,187
Then what will I do?

1325
01:30:52,594 --> 01:30:55,188
I doubt we're going to the same place.

1326
01:30:55,296 --> 01:30:58,527
So, I'll just have to miss it
forever and ever?

1327
01:30:59,667 --> 01:31:01,635
And what if it's not so good?

1328
01:31:02,137 --> 01:31:04,230
I won't be able to fantasize about it.

1329
01:31:08,376 --> 01:31:09,843
I love you.

1330
