I would feel differently.

1331
01:31:26,661 --> 01:31:28,993
I'd stay here. I'd never leave.

1332
01:31:29,831 --> 01:31:33,062
But I've been defending myself so hard...

1333
01:31:33,368 --> 01:31:35,859
...and I don't want to be judged anymore.

1334
01:31:36,271 --> 01:31:39,502
I have this wonderful feeling inside of me,
but I'm....

1335
01:31:40,975 --> 01:31:42,966
I'm just tired of being judged.

1336
01:31:44,913 --> 01:31:46,904
It's okay.

1337
01:31:48,550 --> 01:31:51,041
-I'll miss you.
-I'll miss you so much.

1338
01:31:51,319 --> 01:31:52,877
I love you, Daniel.

1339
01:31:53,454 --> 01:31:54,614
I'll miss you.

1340
01:32:05,400 --> 01:32:06,492
I should go.

1341
01:33:06,527 --> 01:33:08,961
Can you get me the Majestic Hotel?

1342
01:33:15,069 --> 01:33:16,696
Yes, Julia.

1343
01:33:18,706 --> 01:33:21,106
My God, I don't know her last name!

1344
01:33:21,609 --> 01:33:22,667
Excuse me?

1345
01:33:22,744 --> 01:33:26,976
I am in love with a woman in your hotel
and I don't know her last name.

1346
01:33:28,082 --> 01:33:30,016
What's her first name?

1347
01:33:30,785 --> 01:33:34,414
We have two Julias.
Both have "Do Not Disturb" signs on.

1348
01:33:34,555 --> 01:33:37,217
Can you ring through? It's important.

1349
01:33:37,558 --> 01:33:39,458
I'm not allowed to do that.

1350
01:33:39,560 --> 01:33:41,653
But it's very important.

1351
01:33:41,863 --> 01:33:43,421
I'm sorry.

1352
01:33:44,966 --> 01:33:48,493
Can I leave a message then?
For both of them.

1353
01:33:48,603 --> 01:33:50,036
Go ahead, sir.

1354
01:33:51,439 --> 01:33:53,100
Tell them both that...

1355
01:33:54,242 --> 01:33:56,574
...l love them more than life itself.

1356
01:33:57,478 --> 01:34:00,038
I've never met anybody like them...

1357
01:34:01,115 --> 01:34:03,948
...and I'll miss them forever and ever.

1358
01:34:04,519 --> 01:34:06,077
Is that all, sir?

1359
01:34:06,888 --> 01:34:08,082
That's all.

1360
01:34:13,695 --> 01:34:17,187
