1426
01:38:30,451 --> 01:38:33,682
You genuinely feel for this woman,
don't you?

1427
01:38:36,524 --> 01:38:38,754
Why didn't you stay with her?

1428
01:38:40,461 --> 01:38:41,951
I was afraid.

1429
01:38:42,530 --> 01:38:43,462
Louder.

1430
01:38:43,698 --> 01:38:44,960
I was afraid.

1431
01:38:53,307 --> 01:38:54,638
I rest.

1432
01:38:56,544 --> 01:38:58,876
This is a new one on me.

1433
01:38:59,046 --> 01:39:01,776
Sex with somebody and move right on.

1434
01:39:02,483 --> 01:39:05,213
Is that how it works, Miss Foster?

1435
01:39:07,154 --> 01:39:11,386
