I'll do whatever is asked.

1473
01:41:24,125 --> 01:41:25,956
I'll do the best I can.

1474
01:41:26,127 --> 01:41:28,118
Honestly. I will.

1475
01:41:29,363 --> 01:41:31,354
I'll do the best I can.

1476
01:41:32,800 --> 01:41:34,358
Is that all?

1477
01:41:37,972 --> 01:41:39,701
Please just know that I'll--

1478
01:41:39,974 --> 01:41:41,339
Do the best you can?

1479
01:41:43,210 --> 01:41:44,177
Good.

1480
01:41:45,479 --> 01:41:46,707
That's all.

1481
01:41:55,990 --> 01:41:58,390
