1485
01:42:25,686 --> 01:42:26,846
It's early.

1486
01:42:27,021 --> 01:42:29,581
-Is that good?
-It's not good or bad.

1487
01:42:35,062 --> 01:42:38,156
They don't waste any time.
They must need the hotel space.

1488
01:42:42,102 --> 01:42:45,663
How do you like our city?
We do a pretty good job here.

1489
01:42:45,906 --> 01:42:47,373
How was the ltalian restaurant?

1490
01:42:47,475 --> 01:42:48,840
What does it say?

1491
01:42:50,377 --> 01:42:51,537
You're going back.

1492
01:42:55,883 --> 01:42:57,282
Can I say something?

1493
01:42:57,985 --> 01:43:00,977
Because they're sending you back
doesn't mean they're right.

1494
01:43:01,789 --> 01:43:03,552
They can make mistakes.

1495
01:43:05,459 --> 01:43:07,450
Don't let others get to you.

1496
01:43:08,229 --> 01:43:09,890
Just follow what's in here.

1497
01:43:14,001 --> 01:43:16,595
Come on. I'll take you to the station.

1498
01:43:19,573 --> 01:43:22,542
Trams 7 and 8 to onward destinations....

1499
01:43:22,810 --> 01:43:26,473
I'll never get over it.
The organization is amazing.

1500
01:43:26,847 --> 01:43:30,442
All these different trams going everywhere.

1501
01:43:32,319 --> 01:43:36,255
These are yours.
Your boarding card, various ID.

1502
01:43:36,490 --> 01:43:38,321
The things you'll need.

1503
01:43:38,759 --> 01:43:43,093
You won't remember any of this,
so you won't kick yourself forever.

1504
01:43:43,330 --> 01:43:46,766
Just take the opportunities
when they come, okay?

1505
01:43:47,701 --> 01:43:51,603
Passengers going back to Earth,
please board trams on your left.

1506
01:43:52,172 --> 01:43:55,232
Those moving onward,
board trams to the right.

1507
01:43:56,110 --> 01:43:58,271
This is it.

1508
01:43:59,446 --> 01:44:02,609
Good luck. I've got a lot of faith in you.

1509
01:44:10,190 --> 01:44:11,851
I can take that here.

1510
01:44:12,192 --> 01:44:14,854
Keep those and follow the yellow line.

1511
01:44:20,034 --> 01:44:22,594
All trams now operational.

1512
01:44:28,309 --> 01:44:32,040
Trams 7 and 8 to onward destinations...

1513
01:44:32,112 --> 01:44:34,080
...final boarding please.

1514
01:44:42,556 --> 01:44:43,989
Here, sir.

1515
01:44:54,602 --> 01:44:57,537
All personnel, please prepare for departure.

1516
01:45:05,012 --> 01:45:06,001
Daniel!

1517
01:45:06,413 --> 01:45:07,744
Julia!

1518
01:45:32,106 --> 01:45:33,437
What are you doing?

1519
01:45:37,144 --> 01:45:39,135
Sit down! You'll hurt yourself!

1520
01:46:22,990 --> 01:46:24,423
I love you.

1521
01:46:24,758 --> 01:46:26,726
I called, but I didn't know your last name.

1522
01:46:27,528 --> 01:46:28,688
I won't let you go.

1523
01:46:28,762 --> 01:46:29,922
I won't let you go.

1524
01:46:30,431 --> 01:46:32,092
Help! Help!

1525
01:46:40,774 --> 01:46:43,242
Hold on! Just please, hold on!

1526
01:46:43,844 --> 01:46:44,811
I love you.

1527
01:46:45,012 --> 01:46:46,206
I love you.

1528
01:46:50,784 --> 01:46:52,342
Open this up!

1529
01:46:52,686 --> 01:46:54,119
Damn it, open it!

1530
01:46:54,455 --> 01:46:56,616
Please open the door!

1531
01:46:57,124 --> 01:46:59,456
Julia! Wait for me!

1532
01:47:02,629 --> 01:47:04,028
Brave enough for you?

1533
01:47:05,532 --> 01:47:07,796
Open the door! Please!

1534
01:47:15,876 --> 01:47:17,036
Let him go.

